      "part_type": "Hadith",
      "path": "/books/al-kafi:6:8:46:3",
      "relations": null,
      "text": [
        " أَبَا عَبْدِ اللَّهِ ( عليه السلام ) كَانَ يَطْلِي إِبْطَهُ بِالنُّورَةِ فِي الْحَمَّامِ ."
      ],
      "translations": {
        "en.hubeali": [
          "Ali Bin Ibrahim, from his father, and Muhammad Bin Ismail, from Al Fazl Bin Shazaan, altogether from Ibn Abu Umeyr, from Hisham Bin Al Hakam, from Hafs Bin Al Bakhtary that, ",
          "‘Abu Abdullah<sup>asws</sup> used to wax his<sup>asws</sup> armpits with <span class=\"iTxt\">Al-Noura</span> in the bathhouse’."
        ],
        "en.sarwar": [
          "3. Ali ibn Ibrahim has narrated from his father from and Muhammad ibn ’Isma‘il has narrated from al-Fadl ibn Shadhan from all ibn abu ‘Umayr from Hisham ibn al-Hakam from Flafs ibn al-Bakhtariy who has said the following: “Abu ‘Abd Allah, ‘Alayhi al-Salam, would apply lime paste on his underarms in the bathhouse.’” "
        ]
      }
